description:
Listen, we have so much to discuss with you guys this week, we decided to keep it real cozy (i.e. there's no guest). On the table: Some major job changes for both of us; listener feedback to the Kim Kardashian segment from episode 92; Jess's electrifying Clear + Brilliant recap; and a Beauty Book Report on the world's chicest lip balm.
